name: TRUMP NEVER DIE
description: Say hello to TRUMP NEVER DIE: the memecoin so loud, not even the blockchain can fact-check it! Born on Solana and fueled by big hair, big tweets, and even bigger ambitions, $NEVER refuses to lose—just like its namesake. Buy, hold, and maybe even tweet about it—because legends (and memes) never die, they just moon harder. Remember: if you can’t dump, just yell ‘RIGGED!’ and hodl until the next rally!
